{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01XiNMf1uPQBmRAfUmdYhNck","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01BDNaSp4MPgxLAqoze3RMsx","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Roasted Root Vegetable Medley.generated.21.txt","content":"rove that grains can be a star in any kitchen, this beautiful dish combines tender grain with vibrant\nvegetables. The key is timing—each component must be roasted at the precise moment to ensure\ndoneness without overcooking. Many home cooks find this technique challenging, but with practice\nit becomes second nature. Some chefs prefer to parboil root vegetables first, reducing overall\ncooking time. A light tossing halfway through cooking ensures even browning and caramelization.\n\nPay special attention to the garlic—it burns easily and should be added late in the process.\nFinish with fresh herbs to brighten the earthy flavors. This pairs well with grilled meats or as\na vegetarian main when topped with a creamy goat cheese sauce. Store leftovers in a sealed\ncontainer for up to three days, reheating gently in a warm oven to restore crispiness.\n\nRoasted Root Vegetable Medley\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n1 lb parsnips, cut into 2-inch pieces\n1 lb Brussels sprouts, halved\n12 oz carrots, cut into batons\n8 oz beets, peeled and cubed\n6 cloves garlic, smashed\n4 tablespoons olive oil\n2 teaspoons fresh thyme\n1 teaspoon Dijon mustard\nSalt and pepper to taste\n2 tablespoons balsamic vinegar\n¼ cup fresh parsley, chopped\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n1. Preheat oven to 425°F\n2. Toss parsnips, Brussels sprouts, carrots, and beets with olive oil\n3. Season with salt, pepper, and thyme\n4. Spread on baking sheet in single layer\n5. Roast for 20 minutes\n6. Add garlic and stir\n7. Continue roasting 20-25 minutes until golden and tender\n8. Whisk together mustard and balsamic vinegar\n9. Toss with roasted vegetables\n10. Garnish with fresh parsley\n11. Serve warm or at room temperature\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":491,"cache_read_input_tokens":85650,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":491},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e2088c48-e314-46b0-b268-2e09887642e2","uuid":"df8cbb80-2e9c-4c15-9950-5becb7b79eab"}
