st for 20 minutes\n6. Add garlic and stir\n7. Continue roasting 20-25 minutes until golden and tender\n8. Whisk together mustard and balsamic vinegar\n9. Toss with roasted vegetables\n10. Garnish with fresh parsley\n11. Serve warm or at room temperature\n","structuredPatch":[],"originalFile":null}}
